<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 10:07:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将面临的耻辱将远远大于他试图逃避的耻辱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</link><description>比比作为“以色列保护者”的神话已经打破。 “一切都结束了，”执政联盟的一名高级成员本周表示。 “政府将无法幸存”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党发射火箭后，以色列军队在黎巴嫩进行报复；以色列北部城市撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/after-hezbollah-launches-rockets-idf-retaliates-in-lebanon-northern-city-to-evacuate/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</link><description>随着紧张局势升级，以色列为黎巴嫩北部边境附近的居民制定疏散计划 ■ 以色列军队称一夜之间袭击了加沙的一百多个目标 ■ 拜登要求国会向以色列提供 140 亿美元的军事援助 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯： 3,200 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/after-hezbollah-launches-rockets-idf-retaliates-in-lebanon-northern-city-to-evacuate/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>导致哈马斯袭击的失败永远改变了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</link><description>安全机构热衷于敌人被威慑的观念 ■ 内塔尼亚胡扶植哈马斯，而以色列人却视而不见 ■ 多年来忽视巴以冲突的后果，突然付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡仍然相信他能够逃避指责并在以色列最大的灾难中幸存下来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</link><description>加沙边境灾难发生两周后，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡甚至还没有做出接受责任的姿态——与许多以色列高级国防官员不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将向国会请求 140 亿美元的以色列军事援助：“敌对行为者将知道以色列比以往任何时候都更强大”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</link><description>在罕见的椭圆形办公室讲话中，美国总统将哈马斯与普京进行了比较，称“他们都想彻底消灭邻国的民主国家”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 00:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯轮盘赌”：以色列遭受轰炸最严重的城市的居民得不到保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</link><description>阿什凯隆是加沙战争中目标最严重的城市，该城的约 40,000 名居民缺乏适当的保护以免受火箭弹袭击——尽管事实上已经为此编列了资金预算</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 22:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们在达兰萨拉冥想。突然，来自以色列的电话开始涌入”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在战争期间，一名年轻女子返回以色列的家，而另一名年轻女子则在拉脱维亚与家人团聚</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</guid></item><item><title>战时考验以色列的民主</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</guid></item><item><title>睁大眼睛：以色列情报部门对哈马斯的军事集结视而不见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:18:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对抗更强大的以色列的长期目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯真的像伊斯兰国吗？专家讲解</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</link><description>是否有可能与哈马斯合作？十二位研究伊斯兰团体及其历史的学者努力确定它是如何成为今天的怪物的，并提出了行动方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</guid></item><item><title>武装警卫保护本周末在美国校园参加安息日活动的犹太学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</link><description>希勒尔国际总裁表示，我们需要对真正的威胁保持警惕。在针对加沙战争的一波反以色列集会之后，犹太学生组织正在向大学施压，要求其加强安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯袭击后失踪的一些人将无法找到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</link><description>根据以色列军队的最新数据，有 100 至 200 人被列为失踪人员，随着尸体身份的确认，这一数字预计会发生变化。据军方了解，约有 30 名 16 岁以下儿童被绑架</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正式加入美国免签证计划，立即生效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</link><description>以色列入境原定于 11 月 30 日开始，但由于哈马斯袭击后美国驻以色列大使馆暂停签证处理，迫于国会压力，这一进程已加快。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</guid></item><item><title>2007年的内塔尼亚胡：总理对国家安全负有个人责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</link><description>“在像以色列这样的国家，如果一个人不具备某种塑造外交安全概念的能力，你就不能任命他为总理，因为如果是这样，那么这些机构就真正具有统治力；内塔尼亚胡向一个正在调查 2006 年第二次黎巴嫩战争的委员会作证说：“他不控制这些机构，也不指导它们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 18:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人没有安全的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</link><description>以色列最伟大的成就之一是它为本国公民以及世界各地的犹太人提供的安全和繁荣，让他们偶尔忘记自己面临着犹太人的仇恨。从以色列南部到澳大利亚悉尼，情况已不再如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 17:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安曼举行的中东峰会可能已取消，但美国仍应采取严肃的外交行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</link><description>拜登等美国总统周三的访问可能会成为中东外交的一个重大转折点，但问题是这是否是白宫想要的</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</guid></item><item><title>“我没有时间哀悼母亲被杀，因为我必须拯救孩子们的生命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</link><description>被哈马斯绑架进入加沙地带的儿童家属召开新闻发布会，恳求内塔尼亚胡、以色列政府和国际社会帮助释放人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</guid></item><item><title>共和党人将呼吁加沙停火的犹太抗议者与 1 月 6 日的叛乱分子进行了比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</link><description>众议员马乔里·泰勒·格林（Marjorie Taylor Greene）是支持特朗普的支持者之一，呼吁将周三在国会办公室静坐的数百名美国犹太抗议者“关押在华盛顿特区的古拉格集中营”，将他们的行为等同于所给予的治疗致 2021 年袭击国会大厦的人们</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 15:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>